headline: Scotiabank Lowers PT on Invitation Homes (INVH) Stock
summary: Invitation Homes Inc. (NYSE:INVH) is one of the Best Housing Stocks to Buy According to Hedge Funds. On August 28, Scotiabank reduced the price target on the company’s stock to $36 from $38, while keeping a “Sector Perform” rating, as reported by The Fly.
